args: Well, I've experienced lots of things,\nbut I need to try something bigger!
But what should I... Oh! Is that Aoi?
She's from Hinomoto, and a...ninja\nor something? I wonder if she's training?
I don't even know what a ninja IS.\nAlso, her weapon... It's kinda unusual?
Well, I guess this is just my chance to\nhave a new experience with a ninja!
Aoiiii! Can I talk to you for a minute?
Heck yeah you can! What's up?
I wanna know all about ninjas.\nSo, um...what are they?
Hey, cool! I didn't know you were\ninterested in ninjas!
Okay, so the main thing you need to know\nis that ninjas live in the shadows.
Like, you don't go in the sun?
Hee hee! No, it just means we never\nlet the world know that we're there.\nWe protect our masters in secret!
So can I experience being a ninja?
I gotta try lots of different things if I want\nto become an amazing blacksmith.
Of course! Just leave it to me.
They say that teaching others helps you\nlearn more yourself, after all.
And I still have a ton to learn,\nso maybe teaching you will help me\nbone up on all of that stuff.
All right, let's start with the basics.\nYour first lesson is hiding!
So first, you need to stand\nwith your back to the wall.
Now take this cloth and hold it up.\nIt has the same pattern as the wall, see?
Ooo, we get PROPS? That's awesome!\n...Also, I think I see where this\nlesson is going.
Now put the cloth over your head\naaand...boom! You're done.
Behold the mystical ninja art:\nThe cloth of concealing!
You know, for a mystical ninja art that\nseemed sorta...I dunno. Basic, maybe?\nWhat else you got?
Not a fan? Well, there are plenty of\nother techniques I can show you.
Would you prefer to cling to a ceiling\nor hide in a swamp? Both require\ngreat patience, but not much else.
*sigh* I'll just stick with the cloth.
Great! Now put it over your head\nand stand...perfectly...still.
Knowing how to hold your breath and\nstay still is an essential skill for a ninja.
Oh man, I'm not good at staying still.\nHow long do I have to do this?
Just give it your best shot.
Aaaargh! I can't do this anymore!
I'm sorry, but this just isn't me.\nDo you have anything less...ninja-y?
Well, what about elemental escape arts?
Sweet! Then let's go into the courtyard\nso I can explain them one by one.
...So those are the basics.\nDid it all make sense?
I might have understood better if you used\nmore words and fewer sound effects.
Er, but I THINK I get it? It's pretty much\nhow Ramona talks about mana, anyway.
I'll start with the flame one. ...Haaaah!
Oh, I'm not done yet! Raaagh!
Yaaay! I'm a genius at ninja-ing!
The water one was definitely the easiest.\nProbably because I do all the cooling\nwhenever we forge weapons.
You're a natural! I've never SEEN\nsomeone with your potential!
Aw, you're gonna make me blush.
You should totally become a ninja!
We need to start a proper ninja training\nregimen right away. We'll work to\nbecome the best ninjas ever together!
Wait, no! My dream is to become\nthe best BLACKSMITH ever!
Oh, right. I forgot you already had a goal.
But hey, if you ever change your mind,\nyou know where to find me!
Right, I'll keep that in mind...
...Aoi! I know you're on the ceiling!\nGet down here right noooow!
Ha ha! Well done, Renee!\nYou have spotted me again!
It doesn't take skill when you have a ninja\nfollowing you ALL THE FREAKING TIME!
Anyway, have you given any more\nthought to becoming a ninj
Stop asking that! I'm a BLACKSMITH!
Then I'll leave you alone for today...\nBut do not think I will give up so easily!
I'm going to come back here every day\nuntil you change your mind!
